---
title: Tasty Rainbow Trout Linguine with Zucchini Noodles and Red Pepper Pesto
description: In our humble opinion, rainbow trout is a fish that works well in every season. With the addition of a delicious roasted pepper and chive pesto and zucchini noodles ("zoodles!"), this dish is as much of a work of art for the taste buds as it is for the eyes!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/tasty-rainbow-trout-linguine-dbb044ba.jpg
